TI  - Effect of mindfulness-based stress reduction on anxiety in adults
AU  - Smith, John
AU  - Johnson, Mary
AB  - This study examined the effectiveness of mindfulness-based stress reduction (MBSR) on anxiety levels in adults. A randomized controlled trial was conducted with 120 participants aged 18-65 years. Results showed significant reduction in anxiety scores.
PY  - 2023
JO  - Journal of Anxiety Research
