TI  - Exercise interventions for mental health: Systematic review
AU  - Wilson, Robert
AU  - Taylor, Lisa
AB  - This systematic review examined exercise interventions for improving mental health outcomes. Review of 78 studies showed consistent benefits across various exercise modalities.
